1
00:00:44,644 --> 00:00:45,912
I'm Kim.

2
00:00:46,346 --> 00:00:47,781
Is there anything I can help with?

3
00:00:47,981 --> 00:00:49,249
Have we ever met before?

4
00:00:49,983 --> 00:00:51,651
I promised you...

5
00:00:52,452 --> 00:00:54,387
that I would be your memory.

6
00:00:56,456 --> 00:00:57,590
Why...

7
00:00:58,425 --> 00:01:00,325
did you say exactly what I heard in
my dream?

8
00:01:00,326 --> 00:01:01,694
I've told you already...

9
00:01:02,695 --> 00:01:04,464
that I would be your memory for you.

10
00:01:04,731 --> 00:01:06,833
You shoukd go do your job properly.

11
00:01:07,033 --> 00:01:09,335
Even though I know how you feel about Tao Sor,

12
00:01:10,336 --> 00:01:12,539
let me warn you a second time...

13
00:01:13,173 --> 00:01:15,608
Quit messing around with Tao Sor's life!

14
00:01:16,609 --> 00:01:19,779
This is more detailed and complicated
than you think.

15
00:02:03,756 --> 00:02:05,792
Get over here!
- You crazy, man?!

16
00:02:06,759 --> 00:02:08,370
What the hell did you do to my brother, you asshole?!

17
00:02:08,394 --> 00:02:09,395
Do what?!

18
00:02:09,662 --> 00:02:11,197
We gave each other consent!

19
00:02:11,798 --> 00:02:13,332
You tricked him here, didn't you?

20
00:02:13,333 --> 00:02:14,701
You're so heartless!

21
00:02:15,101 --> 00:02:16,469
I didn't trick your brother here.

22
00:02:17,437 --> 00:02:20,372
How about you? How are you taking care of him when you let me take him out here?

23
00:02:20,373 --> 00:02:21,974
Oh, you little...

24
00:02:21,975 --> 00:02:23,742
How can you say that?!

25
00:02:23,743 --> 00:02:25,044
Fucking hell...

26
00:02:25,578 --> 00:02:27,914
Ask him yourself! He's here!

27
00:02:29,549 --> 00:02:30,549
Tao Sor...

28
00:02:31,918 --> 00:02:33,319
I..I'm Talay, okay?

29
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,754
I'm your older brother!

30
00:02:35,788 --> 00:02:36,788
Do you remember me?

31
00:02:37,624 --> 00:02:39,192
How did I get here?

32
00:02:40,059 --> 00:02:40,760
Well...

33
00:02:41,060 --> 00:02:43,062
yesterday the two of us came here together!

34
00:02:43,263 --> 00:02:44,264
Do you remember?

35
00:02:46,032 --> 00:02:47,800
That's enough, stay out of it!

36
00:02:48,101 --> 00:02:49,101
Let;s go, Tao Sor!

37
00:02:49,402 --> 00:02:50,402
Wait!

38
00:02:52,038 --> 00:02:55,175
Yesterday I promised you, that I would be
your memories.

39
00:02:56,442 --> 00:02:57,710
Who are you people?

40
00:02:58,278 --> 00:02:59,279
What am I doing here?

41
00:02:59,479 --> 00:03:00,747
Tao Sor, listen to me, okay?

42
00:03:01,881 --> 00:03:02,881
It's Talay...

43
00:03:03,016 --> 00:03:04,184
your older brother!

44
00:03:06,019 --> 00:03:07,387
You can't remember, right?

45
00:03:08,655 --> 00:03:09,655
Look at this.

46
00:03:12,559 --> 00:03:13,559
See?

47
00:03:14,194 --> 00:03:17,230
This is you. And that's our parents!

48
00:03:17,630 --> 00:03:19,899
And that's me, your brother. See?

49
00:03:22,335 --> 00:03:24,103
We're a family, Tao Sor!

50
00:03:25,038 --> 00:03:27,106
You have to trust me, let's go home.

51
00:03:28,174 --> 00:03:28,741
Tao Sor!

52
00:03:28,942 --> 00:03:29,942
I'm Kim!

53
00:03:30,443 --> 00:03:31,578
I'm the one you said...

54
00:03:31,878 --> 00:03:33,413
you wanted to be your memories.

55
00:03:35,215 --> 00:03:36,349
Memories...

56
00:03:38,084 --> 00:03:39,319
I can't remember anything...

57
00:03:39,385 --> 00:03:40,787
Our memories together!

58
00:03:41,554 --> 00:03:42,755
You can let me tell you,

59
00:03:42,922 --> 00:03:44,591
or I can show you photos!

60
00:03:45,058 --> 00:03:46,058
That's enough with you!

61
00:03:46,392 --> 00:03:47,894
You're scaring him!

62
00:03:48,361 --> 00:03:49,361
No, I'm not!

63
00:03:49,562 --> 00:03:50,922
It's you that's making him scared!

64
00:03:50,997 --> 00:03:52,637
I'm starting to understand Tao Sor now...

65
00:03:52,799 --> 00:03:55,134
how waking up everyday and seeing someone like you

66
00:03:55,435 --> 00:03:57,003
can make such an irritating life!

67
00:03:57,237 --> 00:03:58,837
How's someone like you gonna understand?

68
00:03:59,439 --> 00:04:01,774
Someone that wakes up and doesn't remember jack squat,

69
00:04:02,275 --> 00:04:03,977
you know how panicked they'd feel?!

70
00:04:04,911 --> 00:04:06,471
I've raised Tao Sor since he was young,

71
00:04:06,546 --> 00:04:08,214
How well do you know him?

72
00:04:08,581 --> 00:04:09,349
Huh?!

73
00:04:09,582 --> 00:04:11,217
You're just doing whatever you want,

74
00:04:11,818 --> 00:04:13,519
you don't think about Tao Sor's feelings!

75
00:04:15,054 --> 00:04:18,057
Tao Sor shouldn't even know you, you've ruined his life.

76
00:04:20,193 --> 00:04:22,895
Tao Sor, Tao Sor! Just tell me...

77
00:04:23,363 --> 00:04:25,999
you won't be disappointed
with what happened, right?

78
00:04:28,668 --> 00:04:30,103
We love each other, right?

79
00:04:32,772 --> 00:04:33,772
Right?

80
00:04:33,940 --> 00:04:35,642
Can you just shut up?!

81
00:04:36,876 --> 00:04:38,378
Tao Sor! Let's go.

82
00:04:41,314 --> 00:04:42,314
Wait!

83
00:06:26,452 --> 00:06:27,452
Hello.

84
00:06:28,888 --> 00:06:31,691
From now on, I ask to decline any
clients from Siam Sea.

85
00:06:32,625 --> 00:06:34,865
Including the ones coming for the cooking class as well.

86
00:06:35,828 --> 00:06:37,830
Why? What happened?

87
00:06:39,132 --> 00:06:41,033
Didn't Kim tell you what happened?

88
00:06:42,368 --> 00:06:44,704
Not yet. What happened?

89
00:06:48,374 --> 00:06:49,941
Let's just say...

90
00:06:49,942 --> 00:06:51,744
I don't want to continue.

91
00:06:52,545 --> 00:06:55,548
But just know that your brother
hurt mine.

92
00:06:56,182 --> 00:06:58,084
What did you say? Hurt your brother?

93
00:06:58,351 --> 00:07:00,553
Sis! I didn't do anything!

94
00:07:07,994 --> 00:07:09,362
Mr. Talay?

95
00:07:09,829 --> 00:07:13,533
I think what happened is a personal issue.

96
00:07:14,534 --> 00:07:16,669
We will take care of our people.

97
00:07:18,371 --> 00:07:20,640
But don't let it affect our business ordeals.

98
00:07:21,274 --> 00:07:22,775
We'll lose both our reputations.

99
00:07:23,376 --> 00:07:26,112
Eitherway, I request to cancel the cooking course for now.

100
00:07:26,813 --> 00:07:28,653
I don't need someone to look over the project.

101
00:07:30,349 --> 00:07:32,452
I don't need Kim at my resort again.

102
00:07:33,586 --> 00:07:37,323
I ask for my family's safety first.

103
00:07:39,792 --> 00:07:40,960
How about this?

104
00:07:42,161 --> 00:07:44,730
We'll send over someone else to take over.

105
00:07:46,432 --> 00:07:48,868
Because we already have deals with clients,

106
00:07:49,769 --> 00:07:52,805
we probably don't want them to have an
unpleseant experience, right?

107
00:07:53,773 --> 00:07:54,773
Okay.

108
00:07:55,107 --> 00:07:57,310
But I won't be extending the contract anymore.

109
00:07:58,110 --> 00:07:59,110
Oh.

110
00:07:59,145 --> 00:08:01,013
And tell your brother something for me.

111
00:08:01,848 --> 00:08:03,883
He should never have met my brother.

112
00:08:04,984 --> 00:08:06,953
He ruined my brother's life.

113
00:08:10,289 --> 00:08:11,289
That's not true!

114
00:08:11,524 --> 00:08:12,792
Don't listen to him!

115
00:08:13,292 --> 00:08:15,561
Don't make any excuse!
- Hey! Listen to me first.

116
00:08:16,028 --> 00:08:17,730
Me and Tao Sor are friends.

117
00:08:18,764 --> 00:08:21,767
He called out Siam Sea over this.

118
00:08:22,768 --> 00:08:26,072
If there was nothing serious, he wouldn't have called like this.

119
00:08:27,507 --> 00:08:30,943
We have been in business together for a long time.

120
00:08:31,210 --> 00:08:33,079
We've never had an incident like this!

121
00:08:33,946 --> 00:08:35,748
But once you came in...

122
00:08:40,786 --> 00:08:43,623
Siw. Siw!

123
00:08:44,423 --> 00:08:48,494
Siw! Tomorrow, you go take care of the clients in place of Kim.

124
00:08:48,728 --> 00:08:50,530
Huh? Why?

125
00:08:50,730 --> 00:08:51,831
I don't know either!

126
00:08:52,732 --> 00:08:54,467
I just know they won't have him anymore.

127
00:08:55,134 --> 00:08:56,903
I don't know what he did to his brother.

128
00:08:57,203 --> 00:08:58,404
And from now on,

129
00:08:58,638 --> 00:09:00,640
don't meddle with that resort again!

130
00:09:00,973 --> 00:09:03,376
Otherwise, I'll tell Uncle

131
00:09:03,609 --> 00:09:05,010
to send you back to Bangkok.

132
00:09:05,011 --> 00:09:06,011
Okay!

133
00:09:06,646 --> 00:09:07,680
Send me back!

134
00:09:09,115 --> 00:09:10,955
I don't need to be in this god forsaken house!

135
00:09:13,119 --> 00:09:14,153
Good!

136
00:09:15,755 --> 00:09:16,822
You can go, right?!

137
00:09:17,356 --> 00:09:19,158
Yes, I'll go!

138
00:09:19,559 --> 00:09:22,562
Kim! Kim!

139
00:09:57,630 --> 00:09:59,165
Hey, Kim!

140
00:09:59,432 --> 00:10:02,134
Calm down! Don't be shortsighted!

141
00:10:04,236 --> 00:10:06,205
I was just taking in some air!

142
00:10:06,639 --> 00:10:09,008
I was never gonna jump in.

143
00:10:11,310 --> 00:10:14,313
Don't you know that there's a legend behind this bridge?

144
00:10:14,614 --> 00:10:16,449
Unrequited lovers...

145
00:10:16,983 --> 00:10:18,517
they come here to jump off.

146
00:10:20,152 --> 00:10:21,520
Or...

147
00:10:23,155 --> 00:10:24,890
should i try jumping too?
- Hey..

148
00:10:25,358 --> 00:10:28,394
Calm down! What exactly happened here?

149
00:10:29,595 --> 00:10:30,630
Why...

150
00:10:31,330 --> 00:10:34,333
did Sang have me take over the 1 Day Trip in your place?

151
00:10:38,704 --> 00:10:40,106
The story's...

152
00:10:41,807 --> 00:10:42,807
pretty long.

153
00:10:43,609 --> 00:10:46,078
For the moment, I can't bear to tell you yet.

154
00:10:50,483 --> 00:10:51,917
Whatever's okay with you.

155
00:10:54,387 --> 00:10:55,655
But Kim...

156
00:10:58,024 --> 00:11:00,144
if you have something you wanna get off your chest...

157
00:11:00,359 --> 00:11:01,761
you can tell me.

158
00:11:10,670 --> 00:11:13,110
Have you and Sang ever said anything like this
to each other?

159
00:11:13,572 --> 00:11:14,840
Hmm...

160
00:11:15,574 --> 00:11:16,876
that one?

161
00:11:17,610 --> 00:11:18,611
Hard.

162
00:11:20,346 --> 00:11:21,346
But...

163
00:11:22,615 --> 00:11:24,849
if you got to talk about things like this,

164
00:11:24,850 --> 00:11:26,052
it'd be nice.

165
00:11:34,727 --> 00:11:35,728
Tao Sor!

166
00:11:42,601 --> 00:11:44,103
Don't run that fast!

167
00:11:44,804 --> 00:11:46,272
I can't keep up anymore!

168
00:11:47,573 --> 00:11:48,974
So keep up, Talay!

169
00:11:50,276 --> 00:11:51,510
Tao Sor!

170
00:12:02,788 --> 00:12:05,791
What's wrong?

171
00:12:06,692 --> 00:12:07,893
Forget it.

172
00:12:10,162 --> 00:12:11,263
Let's just say...

173
00:12:12,865 --> 00:12:14,600
I leave the 1 Day Trip in your hands.

174
00:12:16,569 --> 00:12:17,569
Sure!

175
00:12:17,670 --> 00:12:18,670
We all know each other.

176
00:12:27,613 --> 00:12:29,248
Running away all of a sudden,

177
00:12:29,849 --> 00:12:32,318
you had people worried!

178
00:12:34,487 --> 00:12:37,823
Hello, everybody! Today we're here with
" Siwy Style"!

179
00:12:37,890 --> 00:12:42,160
Today, I have my family's own Ya Dom brand to show you guys.

180
00:12:42,161 --> 00:12:45,831
Here's the packaging, let's take a look!

181
00:12:48,834 --> 00:12:51,370
Mmm! Fragrant and fresh for sure!

182
00:12:51,837 --> 00:12:53,172
So, if anyone's interested,

183
00:12:53,372 --> 00:12:56,809
you can click the basket down here, because I've pinned the link already.

184
00:12:57,143 --> 00:12:59,044
See, we have a lot here, everyone!

185
00:13:04,383 --> 00:13:06,652
"Your family does tours, right?"

186
00:13:06,852 --> 00:13:08,988
"Any good trips you'd recommend?"

187
00:13:10,122 --> 00:13:13,125
Oh! I'm gonna be holding a 1 Day Trip,

188
00:13:13,292 --> 00:13:15,092
bringing everyone to learn cooking in Phuket.

189
00:13:15,161 --> 00:13:18,329
Guaranteed fun and delicious meals for sure!

190
00:13:18,330 --> 00:13:20,332
If anyone's interested, you can contact me!

191
00:13:23,669 --> 00:13:25,971
Miss Nao asks:

192
00:13:26,272 --> 00:13:28,107
"I wanna go too!"

193
00:13:32,344 --> 00:13:35,014
Then come, Miss Nao. I'll be waiting.

194
00:13:35,314 --> 00:13:36,682
I guarantee

195
00:13:36,916 --> 00:13:40,085
delicious food, and delicious people.

196
00:13:49,662 --> 00:13:50,262
Tao Sor!
It's Talay!

197
00:13:51,198 --> 00:13:52,431
I'm your brother.

198
00:14:00,773 --> 00:14:01,773
Tao Sor!

199
00:14:10,115 --> 00:14:11,115
Tao Sor!

200
00:14:11,550 --> 00:14:13,319
It's Talay!

201
00:14:13,986 --> 00:14:15,521
I'm your brother.

202
00:14:25,297 --> 00:14:26,298
Are you okay?

203
00:14:27,266 --> 00:14:28,266
It's nothing.

204
00:14:29,802 --> 00:14:30,870
My name..

205
00:14:31,303 --> 00:14:32,338
Is Tao Sor?

206
00:14:33,439 --> 00:14:34,439
Yes.

207
00:14:35,040 --> 00:14:37,476
You're Tao Sor, my little brother.

208
00:14:45,417 --> 00:14:46,418
See?

209
00:14:47,953 --> 00:14:50,322
You live at this resort with your Mom and Dad,

210
00:14:50,890 --> 00:14:51,890
And me too.

211
00:15:05,671 --> 00:15:07,239
Is something wrong? Are you okay?

212
00:15:08,107 --> 00:15:09,241
I just...

213
00:15:11,010 --> 00:15:12,511
had a nightmare.

214
00:15:24,823 --> 00:15:25,758
Um..
Everyone?

215
00:15:26,825 --> 00:15:30,262
Our trip with Siam Sea has now come to an end.

216
00:15:30,562 --> 00:15:33,999
But we have 30 minutes for you to take a break,

217
00:15:34,199 --> 00:15:36,268
please proceed to relax as you please.

218
00:15:36,635 --> 00:15:39,471
Thank you so much! Thank you!

219
00:15:55,921 --> 00:15:57,423
Nao!

220
00:15:58,390 --> 00:15:59,391
How'd you get here?

221
00:16:00,192 --> 00:16:01,860
Wanna take a seat?

222
00:16:04,563 --> 00:16:06,799
Why'd you come without saying anything?

223
00:16:07,166 --> 00:16:09,435
Well, to surprise you! You're not glad?

224
00:16:09,969 --> 00:16:12,304
Of course, I'm very glad too!

225
00:16:21,714 --> 00:16:22,781
I didn't order this.

226
00:16:23,248 --> 00:16:25,517
I did. You want some? I'll feed it to you.

227
00:16:27,086 --> 00:16:28,921
I can't eat Tai Pla curry...

228
00:16:29,154 --> 00:16:30,789
You're a born and bred Phuket native!

229
00:16:33,659 --> 00:16:35,661
What should we do?

230
00:16:36,862 --> 00:16:38,263
You want this?
- Sure!

231
00:16:47,039 --> 00:16:48,941
Mmm! That's good!

232
00:16:51,043 --> 00:16:52,378
It's not bad?

233
00:16:52,678 --> 00:16:53,846
It's my favorite, you know?

234
00:16:54,680 --> 00:16:55,680
Nope!

235
00:16:55,714 --> 00:16:56,348
It's great!

236
00:16:56,682 --> 00:16:58,584
I understand why it's your favorite!

237
00:17:02,321 --> 00:17:02,788
This...

238
00:17:03,155 --> 00:17:04,515
has been on me everyday, you know?

239
00:17:05,624 --> 00:17:07,326
You think I'm here because of luck?

240
00:17:08,560 --> 00:17:10,062
I'm here by my own choice.

241
00:17:13,065 --> 00:17:15,267
Since I'm here, you want your fortune told?

242
00:17:19,204 --> 00:17:21,206
What does this mean?

243
00:17:22,408 --> 00:17:24,710
You luck in love looks really good!

244
00:17:24,943 --> 00:17:25,943
Really?

245
00:17:26,645 --> 00:17:27,312
How so?

246
00:17:27,579 --> 00:17:30,749
It says they'll be a medium to help you achieve your goals.

247
00:17:31,750 --> 00:17:34,185
Medium... like...

248
00:17:34,186 --> 00:17:35,620
Cupid or something?

249
00:17:35,621 --> 00:17:36,422
Yes!

250
00:17:36,423 --> 00:17:39,425
Aww, I thought my love would be good.

251
00:17:39,758 --> 00:17:42,461
Your love is right in front of you.

252
00:17:46,265 --> 00:17:47,766
In front of me?
- Yes!

253
00:17:51,470 --> 00:17:53,005
What's with you?

254
00:17:54,506 --> 00:17:56,341
Let's eat.
- Go ahead!

255
00:18:20,499 --> 00:18:21,499
Chef Mochi.

256
00:18:24,069 --> 00:18:25,237
Tired, right?

257
00:18:25,637 --> 00:18:28,307
Go rest. I'll take care of the rest.

258
00:18:33,979 --> 00:18:35,581
Daiji?
- Hm?

259
00:18:36,482 --> 00:18:37,716
Can I ask you something?

260
00:18:39,718 --> 00:18:41,386
Have you known me since I was young?

261
00:18:42,354 --> 00:18:46,859
Well, since you were 10, I think? If I remember correctly.

262
00:18:47,392 --> 00:18:48,392
Why?

263
00:18:49,228 --> 00:18:50,228
Nothing.

264
00:18:50,395 --> 00:18:51,395
I just..

265
00:18:52,064 --> 00:18:53,899
Wanna know what I was like as a child.

266
00:18:56,869 --> 00:18:58,470
You were a rascal.

267
00:18:59,805 --> 00:19:01,640
Joking! I'm just joking!

268
00:19:02,107 --> 00:19:03,242
You were sweet,

269
00:19:03,709 --> 00:19:04,877
just like this.

270
00:19:05,177 --> 00:19:06,912
You were sweet everyday!

271
00:19:09,348 --> 00:19:10,549
And...

272
00:19:11,583 --> 00:19:12,918
what do I like,

273
00:19:13,752 --> 00:19:14,953
what do I hate,

274
00:19:16,688 --> 00:19:18,357
since when did I stop remembering,

275
00:19:18,957 --> 00:19:20,459
do you know?

276
00:19:21,627 --> 00:19:24,630
Umm, those things aren't important.

277
00:19:25,197 --> 00:19:27,633
Just being happy in each day,

278
00:19:28,167 --> 00:19:29,635
is enough.

279
00:19:32,538 --> 00:19:36,875
That's true, but I wanna get to know myself better.

280
00:19:41,446 --> 00:19:42,581
You still haven't went home?

281
00:19:50,722 --> 00:19:52,658
Hello, Talay.

282
00:19:53,725 --> 00:19:55,227
Talay?

283
00:19:56,195 --> 00:19:58,830
What were we like as kids?

284
00:20:03,268 --> 00:20:04,303
Just like this.

285
00:20:05,337 --> 00:20:06,337
And...

286
00:20:10,075 --> 00:20:11,743
did I dream to be a chef?

287
00:20:12,277 --> 00:20:13,277
Or..

288
00:20:13,912 --> 00:20:15,392
Do I have any other skills like this?

289
00:20:16,915 --> 00:20:18,784
Sometimes, when people ask..

290
00:20:19,218 --> 00:20:20,419
I also get curious.

291
00:20:25,224 --> 00:20:26,658
Hmm...

292
00:20:28,627 --> 00:20:30,667
You've dreamt of being a chef since you were young.

293
00:20:31,396 --> 00:20:33,198
Now you get to follow your dreams.

294
00:20:35,400 --> 00:20:36,435
And..

295
00:20:37,903 --> 00:20:39,705
Do I have a history with the ocean?

296
00:20:46,912 --> 00:20:50,249
Um, I think we should get going. Mom and Dad's waiting.

297
00:20:52,317 --> 00:20:53,585
Take care of the rest, Daiji.

298
00:20:55,988 --> 00:20:56,988
Goodnight.

299
00:21:19,378 --> 00:21:21,546
Tao Sor?

300
00:21:23,081 --> 00:21:24,081
Tao Sor!

301
00:21:25,150 --> 00:21:26,752
Yes?

302
00:21:27,786 --> 00:21:28,954
Umm...

303
00:21:29,421 --> 00:21:31,023
do we know each other?

304
00:21:31,723 --> 00:21:32,723
I'm Mor Kluen.

305
00:21:33,058 --> 00:21:34,226
I'm a friend of Talay's,

306
00:21:34,359 --> 00:21:35,994
as well as your regular doctor.

307
00:21:41,767 --> 00:21:42,768
And...

308
00:21:44,269 --> 00:21:45,637
are you studying for a test?

309
00:21:46,338 --> 00:21:47,338
Not at all...

310
00:21:47,439 --> 00:21:50,559
These days I've been looking through a lot of old research papers, that's all.

311
00:21:51,310 --> 00:21:55,514
Those Freud papers about the subconcious mind, those kind of things.

312
00:21:56,648 --> 00:21:57,683
Freud...

313
00:21:59,284 --> 00:22:00,284
Who's that?

314
00:22:00,619 --> 00:22:03,722
The person who said that our dreams are our true wishes confined,

315
00:22:04,056 --> 00:22:05,157
And to be honest,

316
00:22:05,791 --> 00:22:07,326
he seems pretty off in the head,

317
00:22:07,826 --> 00:22:09,426
but still a very interesting individual.

318
00:22:10,629 --> 00:22:12,097
Some times...

319
00:22:12,464 --> 00:22:14,599
dreams can tell us quite a lot.

320
00:22:15,200 --> 00:22:17,368
Especially the dreams that repeatedly come back,

321
00:22:17,369 --> 00:22:19,538
or ones that are unusually detailed.

322
00:22:21,440 --> 00:22:22,941
Repeated dreams...

323
00:22:24,543 --> 00:22:25,543
Then...

324
00:22:25,911 --> 00:22:28,246
if I dreamt that I fell into water..

325
00:22:29,281 --> 00:22:30,281
But...

326
00:22:30,749 --> 00:22:31,950
not in a painful way.

327
00:22:32,718 --> 00:22:33,718
Like...

328
00:22:34,886 --> 00:22:36,922
gradually sinking and...

329
00:22:37,522 --> 00:22:38,657
everything turned dark.

330
00:22:40,559 --> 00:22:42,260
Can that mean anything?

331
00:22:46,264 --> 00:22:47,432
Sometimes...

332
00:22:47,799 --> 00:22:49,401
it could be a sign of fear

333
00:22:50,302 --> 00:22:51,903
or things that have been unclear

334
00:22:52,471 --> 00:22:53,471
or unsual.

335
00:22:54,473 --> 00:22:56,208
Especially if the dream is cloudy.

336
00:22:58,343 --> 00:22:59,343
Or...

337
00:23:00,278 --> 00:23:03,281
Is me being afraid of the water and the ocean...

338
00:23:03,982 --> 00:23:05,283
because I've drowned before?

339
00:23:08,120 --> 00:23:09,120
When I was young,

340
00:23:10,288 --> 00:23:11,790
I couldn't remember anything.

341
00:23:12,457 --> 00:23:13,725
Umm.

342
00:23:15,427 --> 00:23:19,831
The memories will come back when we're ready.

343
00:23:20,799 --> 00:23:22,067
Then...

344
00:23:23,268 --> 00:23:26,271
that means, whenever we're ready...

345
00:23:28,240 --> 00:23:29,941
the dreams will get clearer, right?

346
00:23:31,877 --> 00:23:32,877
Mm!

347
00:23:34,479 --> 00:23:37,816
Then I won't bother you anymore.

348
00:23:39,351 --> 00:23:40,886
Till we meet again, Mor Kluen!

349
00:23:41,119 --> 00:23:42,119
Okay.

350
00:23:42,421 --> 00:23:44,122
If you dream of anything, you can tell me.

351
00:23:45,257 --> 00:23:46,425
Will do.

352
00:24:03,708 --> 00:24:04,708
Hello?

353
00:24:05,110 --> 00:24:08,180
Hey, we gotta talk. It's about Tao Sor.

354
00:24:13,385 --> 00:24:14,586
Snacks, Mr. Talay.

355
00:24:15,887 --> 00:24:16,887
Thanks alot.

356
00:24:24,563 --> 00:24:25,630
Mor,

357
00:24:26,264 --> 00:24:28,142
about what you said, about Tao Sor remembering things,

358
00:24:28,166 --> 00:24:31,269
about Tao Sor remembering things, just how much does he remember?

359
00:24:35,340 --> 00:24:37,242
It's not a continuous memory,

360
00:24:38,510 --> 00:24:39,711
it's kind of like...

361
00:24:41,279 --> 00:24:42,514
the suppressed memories...

362
00:24:43,248 --> 00:24:44,583
are so deep,

363
00:24:45,484 --> 00:24:48,324
that not even the owner of the memories knows what they're looking for.

364
00:24:50,922 --> 00:24:52,624
And if those memories come back,

365
00:24:53,358 --> 00:24:54,438
would that be a good thing?

366
00:25:01,433 --> 00:25:03,502
If it was a nice thing, then yes.

367
00:25:04,703 --> 00:25:06,423
But if it was something that caused pain...

368
00:25:07,305 --> 00:25:09,908
we'll have to accept that it's their right to remember

369
00:25:10,342 --> 00:25:11,409
according to human nature.

370
00:25:14,846 --> 00:25:16,726
But I don't want Tao Sor to be in pain anymore.

371
00:25:18,116 --> 00:25:19,116
That's up to you!

372
00:25:19,618 --> 00:25:20,618
But I suggest...

373
00:25:21,152 --> 00:25:25,524
sometimes not remembering at all is no different from running away?

374
00:25:25,724 --> 00:25:27,392
Right now, Tao Sor's having weird dreams.

375
00:25:27,559 --> 00:25:30,262
It's a sign that he's trying to communicate with his past self.

376
00:25:31,463 --> 00:25:33,231
If he sees the right thing,

377
00:25:34,165 --> 00:25:35,925
the thing he's been searching for all along,

378
00:25:36,268 --> 00:25:37,948
the memories will come back by themselves.

379
00:25:39,638 --> 00:25:42,674
And if that's the case, wouldn't that be even more dangerous?

380
00:25:48,079 --> 00:25:49,180
I'm just afraid.

381
00:25:50,348 --> 00:25:52,817
Afraid that if Tao Sor's memories do come back,

382
00:25:54,185 --> 00:25:55,554
nothing will be the same.

383
00:25:57,122 --> 00:25:59,524
Yeah, I understand.

384
00:26:00,425 --> 00:26:02,260
Although Tao Sor won't be the same,

385
00:26:02,827 --> 00:26:04,863
but he'll get to be his true self.

386
00:26:05,196 --> 00:26:07,232
Not the version we want him to be.

387
00:26:13,138 --> 00:26:15,807
And what if I don't want Tao Sor's memories to come back?

388
00:26:20,178 --> 00:26:24,215
You'd probably have to to be him a lot more.

389
00:26:24,683 --> 00:26:28,587
So he can focus on the present, and not the past.

390
00:26:44,436 --> 00:26:47,939
Chef Mochi, what are you doing? Not going home?

391
00:26:48,340 --> 00:26:49,474
Oh.

392
00:26:50,241 --> 00:26:52,086
I'm just preparing some Soy Sauce Pork Belly (Moo Hong)

393
00:26:52,110 --> 00:26:54,879
I saw that we'd be making Moo Hong tomorrow morning,

394
00:26:55,146 --> 00:26:56,748
so I wanted to start prepping today.

395
00:26:57,582 --> 00:26:59,718
But we don't have any classes tomorrow?

396
00:27:01,486 --> 00:27:04,055
What? There's no class?

397
00:27:07,192 --> 00:27:09,828
But I think I remember...

398
00:27:10,161 --> 00:27:12,764
a client saying that we'll be making Moo Hong tomorrow?

399
00:27:13,465 --> 00:27:14,599
You remember that?

400
00:27:17,235 --> 00:27:19,604
You must be confused, just wrap it up.

401
00:27:43,528 --> 00:27:45,063
Is something wrong, Mom?

402
00:27:45,163 --> 00:27:47,599
Your brother's looking strange these days, Talay...

403
00:27:48,066 --> 00:27:49,567
I couldn't stop worrying.

404
00:27:50,869 --> 00:27:54,439
Is there anything going on with your brother? Have you guys gone anywhere lately?

405
00:27:56,875 --> 00:27:57,875
No.

406
00:28:04,282 --> 00:28:07,886
He's drawing these strange pictures, I have a bad feeling about this.

407
00:28:11,222 --> 00:28:12,524
It's nothing, Mom.

408
00:28:13,758 --> 00:28:14,926
You don't have to be worried.

409
00:28:16,461 --> 00:28:17,962
I'll take care of everything.

410
00:28:18,963 --> 00:28:23,601
I think maybe we should take him out to do something new?

411
00:28:48,827 --> 00:28:51,796
Wait here for a minute, okay? We're gonna find something to eat.

412
00:28:53,498 --> 00:28:55,800
Wait here, we'll be back!

413
00:29:20,892 --> 00:29:24,496
Tao Sor!

414
00:29:29,667 --> 00:29:30,667
Sorry?

415
00:29:33,037 --> 00:29:34,105
Do we know each other?

416
00:29:35,473 --> 00:29:36,941
I missed you so much.

417
00:29:38,109 --> 00:29:39,109
Do you remember you?

418
00:29:40,712 --> 00:29:41,713
Who are you?

419
00:29:42,313 --> 00:29:43,313
I'm Kim!

420
00:29:50,388 --> 00:29:51,388
Get over here!

421
00:29:51,556 --> 00:29:53,391
Hey, what's this?
- Come!

422
00:29:54,993 --> 00:29:55,894
What's your deal?

423
00:29:55,895 --> 00:29:58,363
Didn't I tell you to stop messing with Tao Sor?

424
00:29:59,297 --> 00:30:00,298
I'm not threatening you..

425
00:30:00,899 --> 00:30:01,899
I'll do it for real.

426
00:30:02,000 --> 00:30:03,434
I really don't understand you.

427
00:30:04,068 --> 00:30:06,628
Just letting your brother remember what happened the day before,

428
00:30:06,805 --> 00:30:07,805
how's that a bad thing?

429
00:30:08,706 --> 00:30:10,266
That's because you don't know anything!

430
00:30:10,742 --> 00:30:12,277
What Tao Sor had to go through...

431
00:30:12,877 --> 00:30:13,945
cause you're simpleminded.

432
00:30:14,679 --> 00:30:15,679
But it's a good thing

433
00:30:16,181 --> 00:30:17,541
that he doesn't remember anything.

434
00:30:18,616 --> 00:30:19,951
Doesn't remember that he...

435
00:30:22,187 --> 00:30:24,122
got with a horrible person like you.

436
00:30:25,390 --> 00:30:26,591
Me and Tao Sor

437
00:30:26,925 --> 00:30:28,226
were consensual to each other.

438
00:30:29,093 --> 00:30:30,962
And I do feel like I love him.

439
00:30:31,362 --> 00:30:32,362
Love?

440
00:30:32,764 --> 00:30:34,465
How can you dare say that you love him?

441
00:30:35,433 --> 00:30:36,668
Look at what you did!

442
00:30:37,435 --> 00:30:39,237
You made him confused.

443
00:30:40,071 --> 00:30:41,506
If I wasn't there that day,

444
00:30:42,073 --> 00:30:44,108
who knows where he'd be by now.

445
00:30:46,077 --> 00:30:47,397
But did he choose to go with you?

446
00:30:48,112 --> 00:30:49,547
Or did you decide for him?

447
00:30:50,281 --> 00:30:51,583
- You little...
I love Tao Sor!

448
00:30:55,987 --> 00:30:57,755
He loves me?

449
00:31:04,062 --> 00:31:06,764
Let Tao Sor forget those feelings along with you!

450
00:31:09,500 --> 00:31:11,202
I've proven to Tao Sor,

451
00:31:11,669 --> 00:31:13,538
that I would be his memory for him!

452
00:31:30,488 --> 00:31:34,525
Whoa, I was gonna bring you some beer,
but you're already set.

453
00:31:35,994 --> 00:31:37,228
You're late!

454
00:31:37,562 --> 00:31:39,130
I was working, yes?

455
00:31:40,198 --> 00:31:41,198
I don't believe you.

456
00:31:45,370 --> 00:31:47,090
You were with your girlfriend, weren't you?

457
00:31:47,438 --> 00:31:48,740
What girlfriend?

458
00:31:49,841 --> 00:31:52,410
So what's with you? You look stressed out.

459
00:31:59,150 --> 00:32:01,152
I miss him, Siw!

460
00:32:02,720 --> 00:32:04,088
Miss who?

461
00:32:04,489 --> 00:32:05,957
Well, who else?

462
00:32:07,358 --> 00:32:08,559
It's Tao Sor!

463
00:32:08,960 --> 00:32:10,061
Ahh...

464
00:32:10,328 --> 00:32:13,998
You mean the chef at the resort?
- Yeah..

465
00:32:14,499 --> 00:32:16,701
Well, if you miss him then do something!

466
00:32:17,669 --> 00:32:19,237
You can't just be pouting like this.

467
00:32:19,737 --> 00:32:22,607
Go see him, or just call him if he's busy.

468
00:32:23,241 --> 00:32:24,642
You gotta do something, Kim!

469
00:32:24,809 --> 00:32:26,277
I'm hammered already, Siw!

470
00:32:26,511 --> 00:32:28,012
What do you want me to do?

471
00:32:28,313 --> 00:32:31,649
Every time I go to him, his brother just pushes me away!

472
00:32:32,350 --> 00:32:35,286
He said that I'm dangerous.

473
00:32:35,820 --> 00:32:39,924
So what're you gonna do? You can't just be drinking beer here like this!

474
00:32:46,130 --> 00:32:47,765
Do you have a better idea?

475
00:32:47,832 --> 00:32:50,234
Each day, he acts more like a stranger...

476
00:32:50,368 --> 00:32:51,888
This is a straight up One Night Stand!

477
00:32:52,203 --> 00:32:53,203
Huh?!

478
00:32:53,871 --> 00:32:55,340
What are you talking about?

479
00:32:55,640 --> 00:32:57,375
Kim, calm down.

480
00:32:58,443 --> 00:33:00,912
So what did he do to you?

481
00:33:04,849 --> 00:33:06,250
1 day.

482
00:33:07,452 --> 00:33:08,753
Tao Sor...

483
00:33:09,454 --> 00:33:11,556
can only remember things for 1 day.

484
00:33:12,690 --> 00:33:13,958
Once he wakes up,

485
00:33:14,659 --> 00:33:17,628
he forgets everything about the day before, Siw!

486
00:33:18,830 --> 00:33:21,432
People like this exist?

487
00:33:23,134 --> 00:33:26,437
Then that means, even if you go see him,

488
00:33:26,471 --> 00:33:29,307
there's no guarantee that he'll remember you?

489
00:33:29,674 --> 00:33:30,674
Yes.

490
00:33:34,579 --> 00:33:35,179
But...

491
00:33:35,380 --> 00:33:37,115
I've actually never tried.

492
00:33:38,616 --> 00:33:39,717
It might work?

493
00:33:44,989 --> 00:33:47,325
You luck in love looks really good!

494
00:33:47,492 --> 00:33:48,192
Really?

495
00:33:48,393 --> 00:33:51,561
It says they'll be a medium to help you achieve your goals.

496
00:33:51,562 --> 00:33:53,964
Medium... like...

497
00:33:53,965 --> 00:33:55,365
Cupid or something?

498
00:33:55,366 --> 00:33:56,366
Yes!

499
00:34:02,273 --> 00:34:03,408
Kim!

500
00:34:03,775 --> 00:34:06,778
I'll be your own Cupid.

501
00:34:12,550 --> 00:34:14,752
Alright, what you want me to do? I'm ready.

502
00:34:15,520 --> 00:34:18,356
Is everyone ready? Today we'll be making Moo Hong.

503
00:34:19,991 --> 00:34:21,359
It's pork belly.

504
00:34:23,995 --> 00:34:25,163
Wait for me!

505
00:34:34,338 --> 00:34:36,240
Umm...

506
00:34:36,674 --> 00:34:37,375
Your name...

507
00:34:37,376 --> 00:34:40,378
Oh, this is the new student that just booked.

508
00:34:40,645 --> 00:34:41,645
Ohh...

509
00:34:43,181 --> 00:34:44,482
Where did you come from?

510
00:34:47,685 --> 00:34:51,689
Umm, her name is Kimchi. She's from South Korea.

511
00:34:51,856 --> 00:34:55,693
And she loves Southern food, so she booked a course with us.

512
00:34:56,127 --> 00:34:57,528
Ohh...

513
00:34:57,929 --> 00:35:00,331
Okay, there's another set available,

514
00:35:00,531 --> 00:35:02,600
you can join the class.
- Thank you so much!

515
00:35:02,733 --> 00:35:04,669
Kimchi from South Korea?

516
00:35:06,337 --> 00:35:09,207
We're gonna be making Moo Hong, and these are our ingredients,

517
00:35:09,307 --> 00:35:12,310
pork belly, garlic, pepper and...

518
00:35:12,510 --> 00:35:14,378
over there are the different seasonings.

519
00:35:14,612 --> 00:35:17,715
You can now slice the pork belly.

520
00:35:52,750 --> 00:35:55,753
Thank you all for being so cooperative.

521
00:35:55,920 --> 00:35:58,089
Let's make another menu soon.

522
00:35:58,356 --> 00:36:00,057
Thank you, Chef!
- Thank you, Chef!

523
00:36:02,326 --> 00:36:04,162
Umm, just a moment.

524
00:36:04,428 --> 00:36:05,428
Why...

525
00:36:06,330 --> 00:36:07,999
do you seem so familiar?

526
00:36:11,402 --> 00:36:12,537
We might have...

527
00:36:12,937 --> 00:36:14,205
Crossed paths before?

528
00:36:14,872 --> 00:36:16,140
R.really?

529
00:36:18,176 --> 00:36:19,777
Would you recall..

530
00:36:20,244 --> 00:36:22,113
The person who acted as your rmemories?

531
00:36:25,483 --> 00:36:27,552
I used to be your memory.

532
00:36:32,690 --> 00:36:33,690
But...

533
00:36:33,858 --> 00:36:35,178
Doesn't seem to be like that now.

534
00:36:36,427 --> 00:36:37,528
W..wait a minute.

535
00:36:38,429 --> 00:36:41,132
Can you tell me about the day we met?

536
00:36:41,432 --> 00:36:42,600
Tao Sor!

537
00:36:43,467 --> 00:36:44,468
Chef Tao Sor,

538
00:36:44,735 --> 00:36:48,239
If you're free tonight, come to Siam Sea's port. You'll know everything.

539
00:36:49,373 --> 00:36:50,373
Let's go!

540
00:36:59,016 --> 00:37:00,318
You good? How was it today?

541
00:37:00,451 --> 00:37:02,086
It was.. okay.

542
00:37:03,387 --> 00:37:04,388
Umm...

543
00:37:05,690 --> 00:37:06,690
Talay?

544
00:37:08,359 --> 00:37:09,360
Tonight...

545
00:37:09,994 --> 00:37:11,395
can I go out?

546
00:37:12,196 --> 00:37:12,730
Of course!

547
00:37:13,197 --> 00:37:14,917
Where do you wanna go? I'll take you there.

548
00:37:15,166 --> 00:37:16,367
Umm...

549
00:37:18,269 --> 00:37:22,406
I'm sorry, the time for Siam Sea's trip is over now.

550
00:37:22,607 --> 00:37:25,409
But the clients in Rooms 504 and 508,

551
00:37:25,676 --> 00:37:28,446
they want to go to the aquarium, can I leave that to the resort?

552
00:37:28,879 --> 00:37:31,082
Of course, I'll have the driver send them.

553
00:37:31,449 --> 00:37:31,816
Umm..

554
00:37:32,316 --> 00:37:34,485
It seems like the driver isn't here.

555
00:37:35,419 --> 00:37:36,419
Really?

556
00:37:37,922 --> 00:37:39,557
Y..yes.

557
00:37:42,293 --> 00:37:44,195
Okay, then I'll take them myself.

558
00:37:45,429 --> 00:37:47,431
Tao Sor, If there's anything, call me, okay?

559
00:37:47,932 --> 00:37:49,133
S..sure!

560
00:37:50,601 --> 00:37:51,601
Let's go.

561
00:38:32,276 --> 00:38:35,613
Even though you can't remember me, that's fine.

562
00:38:47,925 --> 00:38:49,093
But...

563
00:38:49,627 --> 00:38:51,629
can we just stay like this for a while?

564
00:38:54,365 --> 00:38:55,800
I don't know what...

565
00:38:57,768 --> 00:38:59,203
happend to me.

566
00:38:59,804 --> 00:39:00,804
But...

567
00:39:01,238 --> 00:39:04,241
why do I recognize the...

568
00:39:04,442 --> 00:39:05,910
scent...

569
00:39:07,311 --> 00:39:08,713
the feeling on my skin...

570
00:39:10,681 --> 00:39:12,116
Who...

571
00:39:12,750 --> 00:39:14,085
exactly are you?

572
00:39:20,157 --> 00:39:21,559
Why don't you...

573
00:39:22,093 --> 00:39:25,096
use your feelings to answer that question?

574
00:39:34,372 --> 00:39:35,373
Tao Sor!

575
00:39:36,674 --> 00:39:37,674
Do...

576
00:39:38,309 --> 00:39:39,643
you remember me?

577
00:39:44,849 --> 00:39:46,417
No, I don't. Just...

578
00:39:47,518 --> 00:39:48,518
I just felt it.

579
00:39:50,454 --> 00:39:51,455
It's okay.

580
00:39:52,256 --> 00:39:53,256
Because I...

581
00:39:54,191 --> 00:39:56,260
will be your memories for you.

582
00:39:57,194 --> 00:39:58,729
How can I remember you...

583
00:39:59,797 --> 00:40:01,432
I don't even remember who I am.

584
00:40:03,567 --> 00:40:05,035
In that case...

585
00:40:05,369 --> 00:40:06,971
do you trust me?

586
00:40:10,474 --> 00:40:11,842
Trust me, okay?

587
00:40:12,910 --> 00:40:16,213
I'm gonna take you on a trip through our memories together.

588
00:40:31,729 --> 00:40:34,598
In the end, your readings were accurate.

589
00:40:34,765 --> 00:40:36,033
Siwy the Cupid.

590
00:40:45,810 --> 00:40:48,779
For sure, the other thing was also accurate.

591
00:40:49,647 --> 00:40:51,015
Which thing?

592
00:40:53,350 --> 00:40:57,254
The one that says that your love is right in front of you.

593
00:42:00,951 --> 00:42:03,487
When 2 blue whales meet,

594
00:42:03,821 --> 00:42:05,990
it's like meeting a certain person,

595
00:42:06,957 --> 00:42:08,459
in our wide and large world,

596
00:42:08,893 --> 00:42:10,528
that truly understands us.

597
00:42:12,363 --> 00:42:13,531
Have we ever made love?

598
00:42:13,697 --> 00:42:14,698
Do...

599
00:42:15,633 --> 00:42:16,634
you trust me?

600
00:42:17,034 --> 00:42:18,111
Where'd did you find this out?

601
00:42:18,135 --> 00:42:19,135
Oh..

602
00:42:19,336 --> 00:42:20,170
Me and...

603
00:42:20,171 --> 00:42:21,739
Don't tell me...

604
00:42:22,239 --> 00:42:22,973
Kim...

605
00:42:23,207 --> 00:42:24,842
Getting to meet Kim,

606
00:42:25,476 --> 00:42:27,411
is the best thing that's ever happened to me.

607
00:42:33,551 --> 00:42:34,718
And...

608
00:42:35,019 --> 00:42:37,588
how do you know if you've ever had any better experiences?

609
00:42:39,456 --> 00:42:40,958
I love you, Kim!
